criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Prostate Cancer;

          -  Intermediate to high risk of recurrence by D'Amico criteria (Gleason scale > or = 7;
             PSA > or = 10)

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patient refuse;

          -  atrioventricular blockade;

          -  Coagulopathy;

          -  Other procedure at same time.
